- added the ability to randomly position watermarks
- removed the "top-left" part of positioning--meaning that position=50%x50% actually centers the watermark image instead of centering the top-left corner of the watermark image
- added watermark rotation

0.1.1-pre1
- added the ability to conver the watermark image to a transparent greyscale image before applying it to the target image

